== 評價 ==
卡卡西在每次官方[[週刊少年Jump|週刊少年Jump]]人氣調查都進前五名，並多次斬獲第一成為最受歡迎角色。<ref name="PopularityPoll">{{cite book|last=Kishimoto|first=Masashi|title=Naruto, Volume 7|year=2005|publisher=Viz Media|chapter=Chapter 60|isbn=1-59116-875-9|url=https://archive.org/details/naruto00kish_0}}</ref>在最新的民調中，他排名第三，[[漩渦鳴人|漩渦鳴人]]和[[宇智波佐助|宇智波佐助]]獲得前兩名。<ref name="PopularityPoll2">{{cite book |author=Kishimoto, Masashi|title=Naruto, Volume 56|year=2011|publisher=[[Shueisha|Shueisha]]|chapter=Chapter 531|isbn= 978-1-4215-4207-2}}</ref>在[[About.com|About.com]]的2006年動漫獎中，卡卡西獲得最佳男配角。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://anime.about.com/od/toppicks/ig/2006Awards/smale.htm|author=Luther, Katherine|title=Best Supporting Male Character|publisher=About.com|access-date=January 17, 2009|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205234032/http://anime.about.com/od/toppicks/ig/2006Awards/smale.htm|archive-date=February 5, 2009}}</ref>他還獲得提名第一屆“尼克兒童頻道雜誌漫畫獎”的“最佳髮型”，最終輸給了[[凱文的幻虎世界|凱文的幻虎世界]]的凱文。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-03-27/pokemon-wins-nickelodeon-mag-favorite-manga-award|date=February 27, 2009|title=Best Supporting Male Character|work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|access-date=February 27, 2009|archive-date=2021-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211129045520/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-03-27/pokemon-wins-nickelodeon-mag-favorite-manga-award|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[Oricon|Oricon]]的“漫畫大師”民調中，卡卡西以8.4%得票率排名第三。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tokyograph.com/news/id-1184|date=June 8, 2008|title=Oricon: manga masters|publisher=TokyoGraph|access-date=December 1, 2009|archive-date=2010-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101231213338/http://www.tokyograph.com/news/id-1184|dead-url=no}}</ref>卡卡西的周邊商品也已發行，包括毛絨玩偶、鑰匙圈、和限量版小雕像。

一些漫畫、動漫、電子遊戲和其他相關媒體的出版商對卡卡西的角色給予讚揚和批評。Christopher A. Born認為卡卡西對第七班教導，即使必須打破規則也要要團隊合作，以強化[[儒家|儒家觀念]]裡的“仁愛與互惠的重要性”。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Born|first1=Christopher A.|title=In the Footsteps of the Master: Confucian Values in Anime and Manga|journal=ASIANetwork Exchange|date=1 April 2010|volume=17|issue=2|pages=39–53|doi=10.16995/ane.206|doi-access=free}}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]注意到卡卡西戰鬥時的嚴肅及與學生打交道時的悠閒、冷漠形成的雙重性，但承認他是該系列中最受歡迎的角色之一。<ref name="IGNNarutoReader">{{cite web|url=http://anime.ign.com/articles/834/834323p4.html|title=IGN: Naruto Reader's Guide|website=IGN|author=Sparrow, A.E.|date=October 9, 2007|access-date=February 8, 2008|archive-date=2012-02-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65bYe0SmC?url=http://anime.ign.com/articles/834/834323p4.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他們還評論說，卡卡西是他們在動漫大會上看到的[[Cosplay|Cosplay]]中最受歡迎的角色之一。<ref name="IGNNarutoReader"/>{{tsl|en|THEM Anime Reviews|T.H.E.M. Anime Reviews}}嘲笑卡卡西如同其它少年漫畫中典型的“神秘人”，但稱讚他比三位主角“有趣得多”，並認為無論出於何種意圖和目的，整個節目可以直接重新命名為《卡卡西》。<ref name="THEMAnimeReview">{{cite web|url=http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=120|title=Naruto [Review]|publisher=[[THEM_Anime_Reviews|T.H.E.M. Anime Reviews]]|author=Ross, Christina|access-date=February 8, 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618133815/http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=120|archive-date=June 18, 2018|url-status=dead}}</ref>Mania Entertainment的Dani Moure喜歡卡卡西融入第七班的方式，因為他是“一個有趣的角色，有時看起來見怪不怪，卻對一身本領如此精通。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/naruto-unleashed-set-11_article_78617.html |title=Naruto Unleashed Set 1.1 |publisher=Mania Entertainment |author=Moure, Dani |date=September 1, 2006 |access-date=September 4, 2009 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014190225/http://www.mania.com/naruto-unleashed-set-11_article_78617.html |archive-date=October 14, 2013 }}</ref>來自該網站的Chris Beveridge表示卡卡西的個性讓他成為自己最喜歡的角色，並讚揚他與培因的戰鬥，尤其在戰鬥結束後卡卡西獲得“非常人性化的時刻”，使戰鬥中的這一集脫穎而出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/naruto-shippuden-episode-159_article_122399.html|title=Naruto: Shippuden Episode #159|publisher=Mania Entertainment|author=Beveridge, Chris|date=May 6, 2010|access-date=May 6, 2010|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100509020557/http://www.mania.com/naruto-shippuden-episode-159_article_122399.html|archive-date=May 9, 2010}}</ref>漫畫家[[冨樫義博|冨樫義博]]發現卡卡西與學生的第一場戰鬥是《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》第一部讓他印象深刻的情節之一，單單藉由卡卡西在戰鬥中邊打邊讀一本書就能顯示他們之間實力的差距。<ref>{{cite book|last=Kishimoto|first=Masashi|author-link=Masashi Kishimoto|title=NARUTO―ナルト―[秘伝·皆の書]オフィシャルプレミアムファンBOOK|series=Naruto|date=December 4, 2009|publisher=Shueisha|location=Japan|language=ja|isbn=978-4-08-874834-4|pages=74–81}}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]將卡卡西列為史上第15位最偉大的動漫角色，稱“他是個複雜的角色，具有標誌性的角色設計和悠閒的態度，散發超酷的氣息。”<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/02/04/top-25-greatest-anime-characters?page=3 | title=Top 25 Greatest Anime Characters | author=Isler, Ramsey | date=February 4, 2014 | website=IGN | access-date=March 13, 2014 | archive-date=2014-03-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140319014434/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/02/04/top-25-greatest-anime-characters?page=3 | dead-url=no }}</ref>[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的Amy McNulty高度讚揚卡卡西和[[宇智波帶土|宇智波帶土]]戰鬥的動畫製作以及對雙方童年時期的映射。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto-shippuden/episode-375/.78398 | title=Naruto Shippuden Episode 375 | author=McNulty, Amy | date=September 5, 2014 | work=Anime News Network | access-date=June 15, 2017 | archive-date=2017-07-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170727151905/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/naruto-shippuden/episode-375/.78398 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2014 年，系列完結後，[[IGN|IGN]]將卡卡西列為《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》最佳角色。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/top-10-naruto-characters?page=2|title=Top Ten Naruto Characters|date=November 12, 2014 |access-date=June 12, 2017 |website=[[IGN|IGN]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.is/20170712135115/http://www.ign.com/articles/top-10-naruto-characters?page=2|archive-date=July 12, 2017 }}</ref>

卡卡西在《[[BORUTO-火影新世代-NARUTO_NEXT_GENERATIONS-|博人傳]]》中的形象引起了[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的負面反應。他在忍者學校畢業考試的粗魯舉止遭受批評，評論家認為慕留人不該受到如此惡劣的對待。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/boruto-naruto-next-generations/episode-36/.124940|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode 36|work=Anime News Network|access-date=February 28, 2019|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724095728/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/boruto-naruto-next-generations/episode-36/.124940|dead-url=no}}</ref>之後的一篇評論中，[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]批評當前學生[[宇智波佐助|佐助]]試圖與女兒[[宇智波紗羅妲|宇智波紗羅妲]]改善關係時卡卡西給[[宇智波佐助|佐助]]的糟糕建議。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/boruto-naruto-next-generations/episode-95/.143851|title=Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Episode 95|work=Anime News Network|access-date=February 28, 2019|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724072943/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/boruto-naruto-next-generations/episode-95/.143851|dead-url=no}}</ref>

